input-from-web (0.1.0-1) noble; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Flask web UI with mobile-friendly layout.
  * QR code with security token printed at startup.
  * Input methods: ydotool type (default) and wl-copy clipboard.
  * Voice-send: auto-trigger send/clear by dictating command words.
  * Configurable word substitutions for voice dictation.
  * Multi-profile configuration via ~/.input-from-web-conf.json.

 -- Shlomi <shlomi@localhost>  Mon, 10 Feb 2026 12:00:00 +0200
